I updated all my ign packages with the latest nightly builds.  Then, I cloned again the subt default repo, and rebuilt and installed it from scratch.  However, I still see the Gazebo title.

Before launch it, I also deleted all the model under ~/.ignition/fuel/[fuel.ignitionrobotics.org/openrobotics/models](http://fuel.ignitionrobotics.org/openrobotics/models) directory.  Is there is anything else I need to clear out?

ign launch -v 4 virtual\_stix.ign robotName1:=X1 robotConfig1:=X1\_SENSOR\_CONFIG\_1
